Options -Indexes
IndexIgnore *

# REDIRECT ALL URLS THAT DOESNâ€™T HAVE A TRAILING SLASH TO URLS WITH A TRAILING SLASH

RewriteEngine On
RewriteBase /
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !(.*)/$
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ http://barbaratozier.com/$1/ [L,R=301]

## PREVENT HOTLINKING

SetEnvIfNoCase Referer "^http://barbaratozier.com/" good
SetEnvIfNoCase Referer "^$" good
<FilesMatch "\.(png|jpg|jpeg|gif|bmp|swf|flv)$">
Order Deny,Allow
Deny from all
Allow from env=good
ErrorDocument 403 http://www.google.com/intl/en_ALL/images/logo.gif
</FilesMatch>

## ERRORDOCUMENTS

ErrorDocument 404 /404.html

